quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,94,"Boola (ewe Muhammad) mbu, “Nikali mbu litala lia mwikulu elili ewa Nyasaye nelienyu sa mwenyene; ne shini lia abandu bandi tawe, mana khekombekhwo lifwa toto nimuli aba habweene.”"
  2,95,"Ne shibalilikombakhwo (lifwa) tawe, khulwa okhubeela akabaranjilisia nende emikhono chiabu. Ne Nyasaye nomumanyi muno awa abamabii."
  2,96,"Ne toto olanyoola mbu bo nibo bayanza muno obulamu okhushilakho Abatsokaasi; yekombanga mulala wabu mbu yakhamenyibwe emiika iyelefu, ne kata kario elo shilinyala okhumurusia mushinyasio tawe. Ne Nyasaye nomuloli muno khukabakholanga."
  2,97,"Boola mbu, “Ulia yesiyesi uli omusuku wa Jibril, toto ye niye wayishia (Ikurani) khumwoyo kukwo khubuchami bwa Nyasaye, itinyisinjia kalia kaliho imbeli wayio, ne ni obulunjifu nende omwikhoyo khubasuubili.”"
  2,98,"Ulia uba omusuku wa Nyasaye, nende Abamalaika bebe, nende Abarumwa bebe, nende Jibril nende Mikaili, toto awo Nyasaye nomusuku wa Abakhayi."
  2,99,"Ne toto khwakhwishilia ebifune bili habulafu, ne shibabikhayanga tawe halali balia abafunakanga amalako."
  2,100,"Koo, buli nibalaka indakano, ne omukanda mubo kuyisukuna? Ne abaanji mubo shibasuubilanga tawe."
  2,101,"Ne olwa yabetsela Omurumwa okhurula khu Nyasaye, utinyisia akabali ninako, omukanda mu balia bahebwa Eshitabu, kwasukuna Eshitabu shia Nyasaye inyuma wemikongo chiabu opara mbu shibamanyile tawe."